name: Emma Stone Redux
description:
A textual inversion of the actress Emma Stone. Enjoy!

Parameters for success

  • CFG 5-6

  • No LATENT Hires fix, use 4x Ultrasharp or another non-latent instead. (Denoising around 0.2 or 0.25.)

  • Add the word "young" before "3mmaston3" to give her a more put-together appearance.

  • Specify certain hairstyles, as it defaults to slightly shorter hair.

  • Works best on photorealistic models, but can be used with illustrated models too.

  • Works great at 512x768 and 768x1024.
